node.title: 'Sewer of the world': World reacts to Prince Andrew being stripped of his Royal titles
node.description: The Duke of York is on trial for sexual assault
node.content: ["The news of Prince Andrew being stripped of his titles by the Queen following allegations of sexual assault has provoked a strong reaction on social media, with many condemning the former Royal.\u00a0", "The former-Duke of York is on trial for allegedly sexually assaulting Virginia Guiffre, now 38, when she was under the age of 18.", "Guiffre also claims convicted paedophile Jeffrey Epstein and sex trafficker Ghislaine Maxwell would lend her out for sex with powerful associates.", "Prince Andrew has denied all allegations.", "English broadcaster, Piers Morgan, reacted to the reports Prince Andrew potentially be forced to quit his nine military roles.", "Morgan also expressed his sympathy for the Queen.", "Other users say Prince Andrew and Boris Johnson are making the country look bad.", "Users are also expressing their sympathies to sexual assault victims.", "Twitter has called out British Tabloids for the differential treatment of Prince Andrew and Meghan Markle."]
